  <para>
    The <guimenuitem moreinfo="none">Paste As New Image</guimenuitem> command creates a new
    image and pastes the image data from the Clipboard into it. If the data
    is not rectangular or square in shape, any regions that do not extend to
    the edge of the canvas are left transparent (an Alpha channel is
    automatically created). Of course, you have to Copy your selection before
    you use this command, so that you get an image with the same dimensions
    as the selection.
  </para>
  
  
  
  
  
  
  
  


